    • Method Detail

      • provideResult

        protected abstract T provideResult(int resultCode,
                                   Bundle resultData)
        Convert the raw resultCode and Bundle into the result type This will be called immediately when onReceiveResult is called, so you can pretend this is a normal ResultReceiver from this method, should that be useful. This method will get called even if the queue is full. If a Handler that runs on the main Looper was provided to the constructor, this runs on the UI thread. In this case, spawn a worker thread for long-running operations.

                    throws java.lang.InterruptedException,

        Synchronously get a result from the ResultReceiver. May be called multiple times to get multiple results.
        Parameters:

        timeoutUnit - The timeout unit
        Returns:

        Throws:
